{"tid":653594,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"求名 一套有20年以上動畫電影","createTime":"2018-05-05T01:13:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-05T12:23:37.000Z","uid":139247,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"340638a246ed0fc82001b43ca833b7b73ddf6c71","tid":653594,"uid":139247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T01:13:06.000Z","msg":"記得無記好似播過兩次<br />\n<br />\n故事大概講有艘太空船 好似進行太空測試<br />\n個測試要用上幾十年時間 所以參加者都要急凍<br />\n之後艘船停左唔郁 參加者解凍<br />\n唔知點解班參加者圍埋吹水講下自己參加原因<br />\n<br />\n男主角好似係通緝犯 上船逃避通緝<br />\n其中一個男乘客係警察 上船追捕男主角<br />\n<br />\n女主角唔記得 <br />\n其中一個女乘客想向前男友報仇 <br />\n想返回地球後去嘲笑前男友揀錯女友<br />\n<br />\n其中一個船員好討厭自己份工<br />\n因每次出船都用幾十年時間 搞到 D親朋好友疏遠哂<br />\n<br />\n之後就講艘船點解停左<br />\n原來係俾 pat黑色既外星生物入侵 <br />\n依 pat黑色野會食左其他生物<br />\n所以參加者就要搵方法逃去救生艙走人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟住點唔知 記得謝幕完會有隻白貓叫春(好似係)"},{"pid":"7c1ecc53b38cbec72790bdb74a40963467bb6ea3","tid":653594,"uid":116530,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T01:15:21.000Z","msg":"Tom and Jerry"},{"pid":"c68ba81e04d3fd769c7af95c05e877d413194d6e","tid":653594,"uid":26675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7c1ecc53b38cbec72790bdb74a40963467bb6ea3","tid":653594,"uid":116530,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T01:15:21.000Z","msg":"Tom and Jerry"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T01:16:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b154cbc156ebb331a50dc9cfc3bb5c02c0dc0ec","tid":653594,"uid":26675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c1ecc53b38cbec72790bdb74a40963467bb6ea3","tid":653594,"uid":116530,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T01:15:21.000Z","msg":"Tom and Jerry"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T01:16:23.000Z","msg":"秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ffa93fbff344e20f7aee4bf941b81fb79635ecf","tid":653594,"uid":3594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T01:49:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有部分似火之鳥 但應該唔係"},{"pid":"6e900bee6e3cb3dc5db2506145d613d928095517","tid":653594,"uid":3342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c1ecc53b38cbec72790bdb74a40963467bb6ea3","tid":653594,"uid":116530,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T01:15:21.000Z","msg":"Tom and Jerry"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T05:26:52.000Z","msg":"套嘢好唔好睇"},{"pid":"c31166701fe574d4b746cd5e1aa63a9e4c94f02d","tid":653594,"uid":139247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ffa93fbff344e20f7aee4bf941b81fb79635ecf","tid":653594,"uid":3594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T01:49:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有部分似火之鳥 但應該唔係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T05:52:41.000Z","msg":"唔係火之鳥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n記得依套野無記擺係暑假朝早播 <br />\n個陣時無記係個段時間都會播下恐怖野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aec3f3c2a2d0f2a71a0869c0b048074ebfd5e927","tid":653594,"uid":157304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T10:44:35.000Z","msg":"靈貓<br />\n1987年"},{"pid":"c481aa35aa3be303aee758292c543ad9a8e8b78a","tid":653594,"uid":139247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aec3f3c2a2d0f2a71a0869c0b048074ebfd5e927","tid":653594,"uid":157304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T10:44:35.000Z","msg":"靈貓<br />\n1987年"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T11:03:26.000Z","msg":"係依套啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來記錯左好多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c45547b5d8b60a0972c39cac74b7d50152c1f9c1